flowchart TD
  A[Platform manager opens host platform_domains route] --> B{Route-level Devise constraint: manage_platform?}
  B -->|No, unauthenticated or lacks global manage_platform| C[404 Not Found — route never matches controller]
  B -->|Yes| D[PlatformDomainsController action runs]

  D --> E{PlatformDomainPolicy: manage_platform or manage_platform_settings on THIS platform?}
  E -->|No — manager of a different platform| F[404 Not Found — Pundit::NotAuthorizedError]
  E -->|Yes| G[Action proceeds]

  G --> H[index: list domains ordered primary-first]
  G --> I[new / create: build + validate PlatformDomain]
  G --> J[edit / update: modify existing PlatformDomain]
  G --> K[destroy: remove non-primary PlatformDomain]

  I --> L{Hostname unique + primary/share exclusivity valid?}
  L -->|No| M[Re-render form, 422 Unprocessable]
  L -->|Yes| N[201 saved, redirect to index]

  K --> O{Target is the primary domain?}
  O -->|Yes| P[Blocked — cannot delete primary, redirect with alert]
  O -->|No| Q[Destroyed, redirect with notice]

  classDef deny fill:#fce8e6,stroke:#b3261e,color:#5f2120;
  classDef allow fill:#e6f4ea,stroke:#137333,color:#0d652d;
  classDef guard fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#8a6d00,color:#5f4b00;
  class C,F,M,P deny;
  class D,G,H,I,J,K,N,Q allow;
  class B,E,L,O guard;
